<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  Establish Rome’s frontier in untamed barbarian territory. Build a legionary camp, command your soldiers, and carve a Roman stronghold out of the wilderness.
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  You are a Roman legionary sent to the edge of the Empire. In the wild north of Hispania, far from the safety of Rome, your mission is simple: establish a foothold, secure the territory, and survive whatever the frontier throws at you.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="450" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.poster.avif?t=1778073708" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.webm?t=1778073708" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.mp4?t=1778073708" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Start with a small expedition camp and transform it into a thriving Roman stronghold. Gather resources, construct fortifications, recruit and manage your soldiers, and lead your people through a harsh and unpredictable land. As your influence grows, so will your responsibilities... and your path from common legionary to respected centurion.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="450" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.poster.avif?t=1778073708" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.webm?t=1778073708" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
