   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <strong>
   BUILD A ROMAN CAMP
  </strong>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Construct barracks, workshops, and defenses to turn a small expedition into a thriving frontier camp.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <strong>
   COMMAND YOUR LEGIONARIES
  </strong>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Assign soldiers to gather resources, craft equipment, and defend your settlement.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <strong>
   SURVIVE THE FRONTIER
  </strong>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Face hostile tribes, harsh conditions, and the dangers of unexplored lands.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <strong>
   RISE THROUGH THE RANKS
  </strong>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Grow from a lone legionary into a respected commander of Rome’s expedition.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Summa Expeditionis is more than a game:
  <strong>
